longBusinessSummary: Islet Holdings, Inc. offers skincare products in the United States. It provides acne-prone skin products, anti-aging products, berridroxies, botanical products, eye treatments, moisturizers and creams, sensitive skin products, toners and cleansers, and specialized products. The company also distributes skincare products of various other brands. It offers products online. Islet Holdings, Inc. was formerly known as Biozhem Cosmeceuticals, Inc. and changed its name to Islet Holdings, Inc. in May 2009. The company was incorporated in 1984 and is based in Grass Valley, California. It has a customer service center in Arizona.
